      • getNaturalSplits

        Set<ByteArrayId> getNaturalSplits()
        Get the set of natural splits for this index strategy. Not all index strategies need to have natural splits but in the cases that they exist, it can be used downstream to appropriately partition the data according to natural split points from the index strategy.
        Returns:
        the set of natural splits
